headline: One Fed Governor Sees Half-Point Cut in December: Our Top 7% and 8% Dividend Stock Picks
summary: If the Federal Reserve implements a 50-basis-point interest rate increase, it could ignite an end-of-year Santa Claus rally. Now is the perfect time to buy our favorite 7% dividend stocks.
